          <p><a href="https://forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/u/redmagus77">@RedMagus77</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>I loved the discussion of how a lot of the text was trying to grapple with ideas that were new and undefined for the time, and I think a lot of games can stand being revised to update both their language &amp; their mechanics to what we’ve learned since it’s creation and publication.  It’s part of why I love the hackability of storygames!</p>
          </blockquote>
