        <dc:creator><![CDATA[@cosmicwimp]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
          <p><a href="https://forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/u/cosmicwimp">@cosmicwimp</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>Another great episode!</p>
<p>I’ve seen the title of Trollbabe before and sort of discounted it because I thought that the name was a bit goofy.</p>
<p>Regarding the length and density of the text, it reminds me of hearing Epidiah Ravachol talking about putting out Dread and feeling that an RPG book was expected to fit a certain format.</p>
<p>Anyway, the game sounds cool and I’d love to see a stripped down version of the text!</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/t/the-farriers-bellows-trollbabe/2880/2">Read full topic</a></p>
